<topic id='business_definition_reablement_intermediate_care_service.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Reablement Intermediate Care Service - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_reablement_intermediate_care_service">Reablement Intermediate Care Service</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_reablement_intermediate_care_service">Reablement Intermediate Care Service</xref>
 comprises assessments and 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_clinical_intervention">CLINICAL INTERVENTIONS</xref>
 provided to 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 in their home (or 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_care_home">Care Home</xref>) within 2 days of need for 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_reablement_intermediate_care">Reablement Intermediate Care</xref>
 being identified, which aims to help them recover, and relearn skills, and regain confidence and to maximise their independence. For most 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
         <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_clinical_intervention">CLINICAL INTERVENTIONS</xref>
 last up to 6 weeks.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_reablement_intermediate_care_service">Reablement Intermediate Care Service</xref>
 can be delivered by a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_multidisciplinary_team">Multidisciplinary Team</xref>, but is most commonly delivered by 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_social_care_worker">Social Care Workers</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
